{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-challenges-classic-show-tsx","path":"/learn/javascript-v9/workshop-countup/step-4","result":{"data":{"challengeNode":{"challenge":{"block":"workshop-countup","demoType":null,"title":"Korak 4","description":"<section id=\"description\">\n<p>Za sve brojeve veće ili jednake od <code>1</code>, kreiraj blok <code>else</code> i unutar njega, pozovi funkciju <code>countup</code> za <code>number - 1</code> i postavi vrednost rezultata na <code>countArray</code>.</p>\n<p>Zatim koristi <code>.push()</code> da dodaš <code>number</code> za <code>countArray</code>, i konačno vrati <code>countArray</code>.</p>\n<p>Ovo osigurava da rekurzivni ciklus (recursion) konačno dosegne bazni slučaj i terminira.</p>\n</section>","id":"694870bcf3c6874112b6f951","hasEditableBoundaries":true,"instructions":"","notes":null,"challengeType":1,"helpCategory":"JavaScript","videoUrl":null,"superBlock":"javascript-v9","translationPending":false,"forumTopicId":null,"hooks":null,"fields":{"slug":"/learn/javascript-v9/workshop-countup/step-4"},"required":[],"usesMultifileEditor":true,"challengeFiles":[{"fileKey":"scriptjs","ext":"js","name":"script","contents":"function countup(number) {\n  let countArray = [];\n  if (number < 1) {\n    return [];\n  }\n  \n}","head":null,"tail":null,"editableRegionBoundaries":[4,7],"history":["script.js"]}],"saveSubmissionToDB":null,"tests":[{"text":"<p>Morate postaviti vrednost rezultata poziva za <code>countup</code> za <code>number - 1</code> za <code>countArray</code>.</p>","testString":"assert.match(countup.toString(), /countArray\\s*=\\s*countup\\(\\s*number\\s*-\\s*1\\s*\\)/);"},{"text":"<p>Trebalo bi da guraš <code>number</code> unutar <code>countArray</code>.</p>","testString":"assert.match(countup.toString(), /countArray\\.push\\(\\s*number\\s*\\)/);"},{"text":"<p>Moraš vratiti <code>countArray</code>.</p>","testString":"assert.deepStrictEqual(countup(3), [1, 2, 3]);"}]}}},"pageContext":{"challengeMeta":{"blockHashSlug":"/learn/javascript-v9/#workshop-countup","dashedName":"step-4","certification":"javascript-v9","disableLoopProtectTests":false,"disableLoopProtectPreview":false,"superBlock":"javascript-v9","chapter":"javascript","module":"recursion","block":"workshop-countup","isFirstStep":false,"template":null,"required":[],"isLastChallengeInBlock":false,"nextChallengePath":"/learn/javascript-v9/workshop-countup/step-5","prevChallengePath":"/learn/javascript-v9/workshop-countup/step-3","id":"694870bcf3c6874112b6f951","saveSubmissionToDB":null},"projectPreview":{"challengeData":{"challengeType":1,"challengeFiles":[{"name":"script","ext":"js","contents":"function countup(number) {\n  let countArray = [];\n  if (number < 1) {\n    return [];\n  } else {\n    countArray = countup(number - 1);\n    countArray.push(number);\n    return countArray;\n  }\n}\nconsole.log(countup(5));","history":["script.js"],"fileKey":"scriptjs"}]}},"id":"/learn/javascript-v9/workshop-countup/step-4"}},"staticQueryHashes":["3858520367"],"slicesMap":{}}